message: Hey guys! Summer is rounding the corner and we are super pumped for study! Here's a group page so that we don't have to keep spamming the Cru page. Summer bible study is open to ANYONE, whether they are in Cru or not, or from the U or not, so feel free to invite your friends to the page! We will be doing study Wednesdays from 7:30-9:00pm! Hope to see ya'll there and good luck with finals!
